        {
            "id": 5939054,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉汽車零組件收到關稅豁免暗示 聯手「輝積」股漲逾200點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股四大指數周一紅，輝達傳出和台積電等台廠合作夥伴攜手在美國建立 AI 超級電腦的本土供應鏈、美國總統暗示 25% 汽車零件關稅豁免，帶動台股今 (15) 日開盤上漲近百點，以 19609.9 點開出，早盤震盪走高，漲逾 200 點，來到 19700 點之上，不過估量僅約 3000 億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>晶片設計大廠輝達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 14 日宣布，將與台積電等合作夥伴攜手，在美國建立 AI 超級電腦的本土供應鏈，首度實現「完全在美國境內生產的 AI 超級電腦」，最快 12 至 15 個月開始量產，合作夥伴包括台廠台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)、緯創（3431-TW）和日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 旗下矽品，相關個股早盤均應聲上漲。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股方面，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 今日開 874 元、上漲 9 元或 1%，聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 及日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 等也走揚，不過，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 走跌。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昨日強勢的代工族群中，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、仁寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2324-TW</a>)、英業達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2356:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2356\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2356-TW</a>) 等均回檔，緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>) 則續漲 4%，欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>) 也續強漲逾 6%、健策 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3653:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3653\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3653-TW</a>) 等漲約半根停板。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而美國總統川普暗示可能豁免 25% 汽車零組件關稅，激勵相關類股，和大 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1536:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1536\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1536-TW</a>)、堤維西 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1522:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1522\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1522-TW</a>)、耿鼎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1524:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1524\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1524-TW</a>)、大億 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1521:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1521\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1521-TW</a>)、虎山 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7736:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7736\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7736-TW</a>) 等均攻上漲停，胡連 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6279:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6279\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6279-TW</a>)、正道 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1506:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1506\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1506-TW</a>)、帝寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6605-TW</a>) 等也漲 6-7%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
